{"tid":542731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【毒link出沒注意】送5000對鞋咁著數？adidas︰了解中","createTime":"2018-01-27T18:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T08:44:28.000Z","uid":142405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e6da35a8e1808bd805c0d6425d450f02d73a6561","tid":542731,"uid":142405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T18:40:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180128/57762001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57762001&d=rexxOVisv75aJtbrIXBXjS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=16805551\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57762001&h=93d629ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180128/57762001</a><br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp近日瘋傳一段「有毒」的連結信息，內容大意是adidas慶祝93週年，將會免費送出5,000對鞋，並附有一個網址。有網民稱按下該網址後，會轉到一個網站，共需要回答一個問題，其後便出現一段文字，指事主有資格獲得「免費一雙鞋子」，但首先要「通過WhatsApp分享給你的20個朋友/小組」，然而選擇鞋子尺寸及輸入地址，3日後就會收到免費鞋。<br />\n<br />\n「送鞋」事件於fb瘋傳，有人聲稱不少人按了連結，該信息被自動轉發給其朋友，他擔心手機內的資料被人盜取。而有眼利的網民發現，連結中的網址adidas的i字有異，呼籲大家不要亂開。<br />\n<br />\n就多民市民指收到有關「我們正在慶祝我們的93週年，並免費贈送5000雙鞋」短訊，要求填下地址及鞋碼資料，然後轉發便有機會獲獎的短訊，《蘋果》已就事件向adidas香港查詢，對方表示了解中，知情人士提醒市民小心，不要隨便填寫個人資料，與及開啟及轉發來歷不明短訊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517060883_c24c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517060883_c24c.jpg&h=979ecfde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517060881_8c5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517060881_8c5a.jpg&h=afd5debd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3642b3526547e99ed66e70a8d476ae4204e1dedb","tid":542731,"uid":142405,"like":1,"dislike"